### Indicator Development Plan
- 12 sophisticated indicators planned
- Based on Smart Money Concepts and Wyckoff
- Focus on institutional activity detection
- See `claude/tasks/task-tracker.md` for full list

### Storage Strategy
- Tiered storage approach designed (ADR-001)
- Hot/Warm/Cold/Archive tiers
- 97% storage reduction possible
- Implementation after indicators work

### Environment
- MongoDB required (see .env for connection string)
- Python 3.12+ with venv
- No Docker yet (keeping it simple)
